{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Give up films, everybody thinks I'm crazy, and I move to Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I move to Australia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I live there fore six years, and all I do is teach people how to make the most of their lives, how to come to a deeper sense of understanding themselves.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's another journey for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the end of that time--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "End of that time I met my present wife, who I meet in Australia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's Belgian.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's traveling through Australia when we meet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] joins me in the work I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We leave Australia eventually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We come back to the states, live in New York for about two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we move out here to Los Angeles where I-- I come out here to write a film for Richard Dreyfuss, who I've known from New York days, and have been living here ever since.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Primarily writing, occasionally still doing workshops, rarely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You never lose-- I'm sure I'll go back to it again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, it's like Shane when he hangs up his guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You never stop being a teacher anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my writing is about discovering yourself anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything I write is about that in one form or another.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's a very good question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that's been happening for me very strongly in the last few years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never-- I don't feel it's a process that completes itself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's one of the things I used to teach people is that there is no final place you get to and that where you sit in like some perfect sauna or something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you just sit back and relax.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it's always the journey continues till the moment you stop breathing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
